{"tid":2268742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共官姚勳智判起底男囚兩年","createTime":"2020-11-03T04:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T11:50:34.000Z","uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69ecb2a8f570b0409158d8636241286b860a1a8e","tid":2268742,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/TZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FTZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Ernp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=e4d65bfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FTZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M%2F&h=058641c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/TZLUFWIQRRCUZN56LIBOVEQA5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港電訊（HKT）男技術員涉擅自登入公司電腦，搜尋及擷取警員家屬資料，再向Telegram「老豆搵仔」頻道發佈。技術員早前在區域法院經審訊後，被裁定不誠實取用電腦等四項罪名成立。法官姚勳智今判刑時指社會事件令警民關係變得緊張，警員家屬資料被發佈至網上，對執法者構成嚴重心理影響，亦對無辜家屬造成極大心理困擾，明言難以接納被告求情稱只因一時衝動才犯案的說法，故須判處阻嚇性刑罰，判監兩年。"},{"pid":"e3c316d76eb270b7d5b17fe137c72a4693cef4d7","tid":2268742,"uid":246828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"尋日馬道立先話法治係基石<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef168835cd75047f1ffd676ced00c847f9206137","tid":2268742,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢係咪真係咁重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f52c85a0b3a6569cfe433022cf8c4e7a9d246","tid":2268742,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef168835cd75047f1ffd676ced00c847f9206137","tid":2268742,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢係咪真係咁重要<img src=